---
title: Chicken & Snow Pea Stir-Fry with Jasmine Rice & Sesame Seeds
description: Step aside, same-old stir-fry. Tonight are you in for a treat! This one is extra special thanks to crisp snap peas and juicy browned chicken stirred into a sweet soy chili sauce. Serve everything over fluffy, buttery rice, sprinkle on some sesame seeds, and dinner is as easy as it is delicious.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-snow-pea-stir-fry-c8ee65c2.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/chicken-snow-pea-stir-fry-610a9de4abb908036618a1c0-d03cb427.pdf
course: main course
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
cuisine: Asian
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/chicken-snow-pea-stir-fry-610a9de4abb908036618a1c0
time required: 20 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 620 kcal
